OL,7,FVideo footage has been released of
OL,8,FCity Council staff being abused while
OL,9,Fcarrying out their jobs.
OL,11,FThe body-cam footage, worn by a
OL,12,Fparking warden, captures the moment
OL,13,Fwhen two parking wardens were verbally
OL,14,Fand physically assaulted as they were
OL,15,Fpatrolling Victory Road and ticketing
OL,16,Fcars that were illegally parked.
