OL,7,FThe authority says a member of the
OL,8,Fpublic became verbally abusive towards
OL,9,Fthe officers, and physically assaulted
OL,10,Fone of them by throwing him to the
OL,11,Fground, after seeing a ticket on his
OL,12,Fvan.
OL,14,FCoventry City Council posted the
OL,15,Ffootage to highlight the extent of
OL,16,Fabuse faced by frontline Council staff.
OL,18,FIt was captured by one of the body
OL,19,Fcameras that are worn by all the
OL,20,Fcity's parking wardens.
