OL,7,FCouncillors said the cameras act as a
OL,8,Fdeterrent and help reduce cases of
OL,9,Faggression towards officers, but they
OL,10,Fcan also capture audio and video
OL,11,Ffootage that can be used as evidence
OL,12,Fby the Council or police to assist
OL,13,Fwith investigations and prosecutions.
OL,15,FThe Council's Civil Enforcement
OL,16,FOfficers reported an increased number
OL,17,Fof incidents in 2023.
