OL,7,FMale and female officers have been
OL,8,Fviolently attacked, including being
OL,9,Fpunched, kicked and spat at and being
OL,10,Fdriven at by speeding vehicles.
OL,12,FThey have also had full drinks bottles
OL,13,Fand cans thrown at them, as well as
OL,14,Fliquids, eggs, and even a road sign.
