OL,7,F"Abuse in any form against Council
OL,8,Fstaff will not be tolerated and legal
OL,9,Faction will be taken."
OL,11,FWe are there to help and support
OL,12,Fresidents and we thank the vast
OL,13,Fmajority of those for the way they
OL,14,Fwork with us, but the message to the
OL,15,Fabusive minority is now clear ` we
OL,16,Fwill inform police and we will look to
OL,17,Fprosecute where possible to protect
OL,18,Four staff."
